    As of release 2.0. Please use RowDiscussionResources or SheetDiscussionResources

    As of release 2.0. Please use RowDiscussionResources or SheetDiscussionResources
    com.smartsheet.api.AttachmentResources
    As of release 2.0. Please use AttachmentVersioningResources instead
    com.smartsheet.api.AttachmentResources.attachNewVersion​(long, File, String)
    As of release 2.0. Please use AttachmentVersioningResources instead

    As of release 2.0. Please use SheetCommentResources instead

    As of release 2.0. Please use SheetCommentResources instead

    As of release 2.0. Please use SheetCommentResources instead
    com.smartsheet.api.CommentResources.deleteComment​(long, long)
    As of release 2.0. Please use SheetCommentResources instead
    com.smartsheet.api.CommentResources.getComment​(long, long)
    As of release 2.0. Please use SheetCommentResources instead

    As of release 2.0. Please use the corresponding method in the [Row/Sheet/etc]AttachmentResources classes
    com.smartsheet.api.ShareResources.listShares​(long, PaginationParameters)
    As of release 2.0. Please use the other listShares method in this class and pass `includeWorkspaceShares` as `false`
    com.smartsheet.api.SheetResources.createUpdateRequest​(long, MultiRowEmail)
    As of release 2.0. Please use SheetUpdateRequestResources instead.

    As of release 2.0. Please use UserResources instead
    com.smartsheet.api.SheetRowResources.deleteRow​(long, long)
    as of API 2.0.2 release, replaced by SheetRowResources.deleteRows(long, Set, boolean)
    com.smartsheet.api.SheetRowResources.sendRow​(long, long, RowEmail)
    as of API V2.0.2, replaced by SheetRowResources.sendRows(long, MultiRowEmail)
    com.smartsheet.api.WorkspaceResources.copyWorkspace​(long, ContainerDestination, EnumSet<WorkspaceCopyInclusion>, EnumSet<WorkspaceRemapExclusion>, EnumSet<CopyExclusion>)
    As of release 2.0. `excludes` param is deprecated. Please use the `copyWorkspace` method with `includes` instead.
